{"_path":"/_lood/debora-vaarandi-saaremaa-kohal","_dir":"_lood","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"Saaremaa kohal","description":"Seal ta on. Siit vaadates alla nende valgete pilvede seest.","layout":"story-page","author":"Debora Vaarandi, Saaremaal kasvanud ja õppinud luuletaja","images":[{"src":"debora-vaarandi-saaremaa-kohal.webp"}],"origin":"“Saaremaa kohal” (1958), kogu “Merelaule sajast suust ja sulest”, Koolibri, 2011.","tags":["Saaremaa"],"genre":["luule"],"person":["Debora","kadakas"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"On midagi nimetu-kallist, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmida seletada ei saa, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nses kõlas karehallis. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nHea on lausuda: Saaremaa!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Seal ta on. Siit vaadates alla "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nnende valgete pilvede seest, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nnäen, kuidas ta rahutu kallas "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nnüüd lahku lööb säravast veest."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Veel ta lahtede sinasse upub, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nüksnes laiud on nähtaval "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nnagu väikesed kollased nupud "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmeremaast, mis lainete all."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ja üle siis kadakalaante "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nkord valgust, kord varjusid käib. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nTuul tolmuga lehvitab maanteel "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nvahuviirgudes sätendab väin."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Seda tuult ja ta lõhnu ma tunnen - "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmetsakohaga jootis ta mind "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nvõi tungis mu lapseunne "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nkui ööde ja tormide hing."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nende väljade tumedad toonid "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nIkka õhtu eel kiirgama lõid, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nolid lindude huiked kui soovid, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nRännukihku nad endaga tõid."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ehk praegugi silmil suuril, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nnagu kivile tardunud näkk, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nüks väike tüdruk seal uurib, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nkus on pilvis see põrisev täpp."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ja äkitselt mõistmatu, palav, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nhull igatsus raputab last. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nTa jookseb, mis võta